dmca.title: SEO Image complains its text has been outsourced
dmca.body:
October 25, 2005

Dear Google Customer Support Professionals,

1)	The copyrighted work at issue is the text that appears on: http://www.seoimage.com/seo_services.html

2)	Search Query:
"a technique of Design, HTML coding, scripting, link popularity building and strategic placement of keywords
